data.event: In 2011, it had one residential community and ten villages under its administration.

Most of the Manchu (Man) live in the central part of the province, in the vicinity of Jilin and Sipingmunicipalities; in addition, the Yitong Man Autonomous County was established in 1988 some 45 miles (70 km) south of Changchun.
